---

<ContentSection title="Skills" id="compatibility">
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    Proficient in a wide range of DevOps tools, including <span class="text-primary">Docker, Kubernetes, Jenkins, Terraform, and Git</span>. for seamless automation and orchestration. Experienced in leveraging monitoring tools like{" "}
    <span class="text-primary">Prometheus, Grafana, and ELK Stack</span>
    to ensure system reliability and <span class="text-primary">performance</span>.
  </Fragment>
  <CompatibilityList
    items={frameworks}
    title="Frameworks"
    url="https://github.com/imranxs"
  />
